metadata.name: The Wedding of Sun and Moon
metadata.description:
🌕🤍🌞🌿🦋⛅️🌤
What anything it the real world that can’t happen.
In MUANGMULUS’s WORLD, they will have been real. 
This is “The wedding of Sun and Moon” that in the real world  barely happen
But don’t in here .This artwork create by inspire form story that someone told me 
“Sun and Moon never met and stay together”  So ,In my world I want to create artwork  form them because Here is land of magic. You try to imagine that the Sun come meet to the Moon. For talk about conversation ,for love ,for wedding. For me, 
I so happy when I see my artwork and  take story from artwork .So happy
